Register to watsonx.ai
https://eu-de.dataplatform.cloud.ibm.com/registration/stepone?context=wx&preselect_region=true

Install Python 3.11 on your notebook (any other dev environment like Visual Studio or PyCharm)

Upgrade pip to this version:
Pip 3.23.1
pip install --upgrade pip

Install below python packages:
pip install langchain
pip install wget
pip install sentence-transformers
pip install chromadb==0.3.29
pip install "ibm-watson-machine-learning>=1.0.327"
pip install "pydantic==1.10.0"
pip install streamlit
